line_1: Has brought back his Paternal Coat, inlarg'd
See his proud Standard o're his Tent enlarg'd!
line_2: With bloated Toads, an odious Bearing, charg'd.

line_1: And Thou, Imperial Windsor, stand inlarg'd,
line_2: With all the Monarch's Trophies charg'd:

line_1: When copiously supplied, then most enlarged,
line_2: Still to be fed, and not to be surcharged.

line_1: Ill grounded Maxims by false Gloss enlarg'd,
line_2: And captious Science against Reason charg'd.

line_1: With rich instruction, and a soul enlarged.
line_2: And brings at his return a bosom charged,

line_1: And on the pris'ner's crimes enlarg'd —
line_2: The pleader rose with brief full charg'd,
